_codex_state.json
.codex/

# Heavy data — pipeline outputs and raw inputs stay out of the repo
Reports/
Unzipped/
Zipped/
Raw/
Inventory*/
SpaceWeather/
External/
*.parquet
*.joblib
*.pkl
*.npz
*.h5
*.gz
*.zip

# Allowlist: keep tiny test fixtures
!tests/data/**/*.parquet
!tests/data/**/*.csv
!tests/data/**/*.clk

# Logs
*.log
Logs/
tmp/
tmp_*/
